Quantum Soul Theory
----------------------------------------------
Definitions
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' Observable System
Any system within the physical Universe that can be observed.

' Quantum Existence
A state in which something that has existed, no longer exists within the physical Universe, and can not be observed, but still exists as a memory of sorts, this mainly applies to anything with an Electrical System (brain/nervous system), but there is a possibility any system that has existed may become a Quantum Existence, think universal memory.

' Unobservable Quantum System
Any system that has existed within the physical Universe that can no longer be observed, but is in a state of Quantum Existence

Theory/Example
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The human body, and mainly the brain, has an Electrical System, a consciousness is created throughout said human's lifespan, and is always changing, said consciousness can not be observed, as it is a non-physical abstraction of the brain/nervous system and it's input/output, a "software" so to speak, since it can not be observed, it can not be destroyed when death occurs to said human, said conscious exists, but as a Quantum Existence, and since said conscious can no longer be observed, and does not physically exist, said conscious may be able to create and edit it's own reality, something akin to a "God".

Possible applications and extensions
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
' (Extra)Universal Memory
' Resonance
' "God"
' Casualty, rewriting
' Searching Universal Memory through Resonance
' Shifting above, below, and to different quantum existences (Parallel/Multiple Universe Theory)
